(4, 1, '2017-10-04 11:53:48', '2017-10-04 11:53:48', '{\n    "ensemble::logo_upload": {\n        "value": "http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//wp-content/themes/ensemble/images/logo_ensemble-health-partners.png",\n        "type": "theme_mod",\n        "user_id": 1\n    }\n}', '', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', '254eb9da-5e24-479f-a331-f73168713658', '', '', '2017-10-04 11:53:48', '2017-10-04 11:53:48', '', 0, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//2017/10/04/254eb9da-5e24-479f-a331-f73168713658/', 0, 'customize_changeset', '', 0),
(5, 1, '2017-10-04 11:54:40', '2017-10-04 11:54:40', 'This is an example page. It''s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I''m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin'' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href="http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//wp-admin/">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!', 'Sample Page', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-04 11:54:40', '2017-10-04 11:54:40', '', 2, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//2017/10/04/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(6, 1, '2017-10-04 11:54:48', '2017-10-04 11:54:48', '<div class="cushycms">\r\n<h1>Solutions born from experience, not theory</h1>\r\n<p class="emphasized">Our vision is to spur innovation within revenue cycle using a proven operational model, paired with technology, to provide predictable, actionable and solution-driven approaches to the complex issues of revenue cycle.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Pressure on hospitals has never been greater.</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>The shift of responsibility from payor to patient in the form of higher out-of-pocket costs</li>\r\n 	<li>Reimbursement rate reductions from all payor sources</li>\r\n 	<li>High fixed and variable costs</li>\r\n 	<li>Patient satisfaction and its impact on future reimbursement rates</li>\r\n 	<li>The rapid evolution toward¬†value-based reimbursement models of the future</li>\r\n 	<li>Maintaining compliance with a shifting regulatory landscape</li>\r\n 	<li>Improving clinical outcomes and the quality of care delivered</li>\r\n 	<li>The need for providers to increase operational efficiencies</li>\r\n 	<li>Revenue leakage</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAll of our associates have earned the Certified Revenue Cycle Representatives designation from HFMA, and we use Lean Six Sigma methodologies. We take a three-pronged approach‚Äîoperational and process best practices, analytics and technology‚Äîto every challenge, which allows us to see the big picture and ensure the upstream processes are corrected and our clients know how to sustain the results. Collaborative partnership allows us to focus on our client''s operational and financial goals while allowing them to focus their time and resources on caring for patients, families and communities.\r\n<div class="half-column cta">\r\n<h2>Our Story</h2>\r\nWe''ve been on your side. Now we''re leveraging our expertise to help hospitals and providers. <a href="http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//our-story/">Read more.</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="half-column cta">\r\n<h2>Our Team</h2>\r\nMeet our experienced and results-driven leaders. <a href="http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//our-team/">Read more.</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n</div>', 'About', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about', '', '', '2017-10-05 05:18:10', '2017-10-05 05:18:10', '', 0, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//?page_id=6', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(7, 1, '2017-10-04 11:54:48', '2017-10-04 11:54:48', '', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '6-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-04 11:54:48', '2017-10-04 11:54:48', '', 6, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//2017/10/04/6-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(8, 1, '2017-10-04 11:55:00', '2017-10-04 11:55:00', '<div class="cushycms"><h1>Creating value for our clients by using our experience, hands-on approach, and alignment with what matters to our clients</h1>\r\n\r\n<p><br>\r\nFrom a provider''s standpoint, it''s an age-old challenge: working with vendors and consultants who have good intentions, but are focused on a singular task or function within the revenue cycle and don''t always have the experience or alignment with the provider to ensure that the upstream root cause is identified and corrected along with understanding the impact on the entire revenue cycle. In many cases, vendors are incentivized to correct issues in retrospect, not to help identify and hardwire a solution that prevents further downstream issues.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After years of working on the hospital and physician operations side and seeing great opportunity within revenue cycle to align the efforts of vendors and consultants with the long terms success of the organization, we set out to create a better way. We built a team of experienced hospital and physician revenue cycle leaders who not only understand in detail each segment of the revenue cycle but who have also personally been on the frontlines in helping solve many of the challenges in revenue cycle. Our partners and consultants have the unique ability to build relationships and connections with our clients because their backgrounds are similar and their interests are aligned. We believe that our people are our greatest asset and therefore take great care in selecting our team members.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Experience and passion for what we do and our approach toward partnership is what sets us apart. Since we''ve been on the provider side, our ability to analyze, develop strategy and execute on that strategy from a real-world point of view drives sustainable, long-lasting results that we can all be proud of.</p>\r\n</div>', 'Our Story', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'our-story', '', '', '2017-10-05 05:19:28', '2017-10-05 05:19:28', '', 0, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//?page_id=8', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(9, 1, '2017-10-04 11:55:00', '2017-10-04 11:55:00', '', 'Our Story', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '8-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-04 11:55:00', '2017-10-04 11:55:00', '', 8, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//2017/10/04/8-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(10, 1, '2017-10-04 11:55:08', '2017-10-04 11:55:08', '[team-bio]', 'Our Team', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'our-team', '', '', '2017-10-05 06:14:34', '2017-10-05 06:14:34', '', 0, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//?page_id=10', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(11, 1, '2017-10-04 11:55:08', '2017-10-04 11:55:08', '', 'Our Team', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-04 11:55:08', '2017-10-04 11:55:08', '', 10, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//2017/10/04/10-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(12, 1, '2017-10-04 11:55:30', '2017-10-04 11:55:30', '<div class="cushycms"><h1>Proven solutions</h1>\r\n\r\n<p class="emphasized">Unlike the traditional consulting or contingency model, we partner with your hospital to go beyond the operational task at hand, and we help our clients by ensuring the upstream processes are identified and that our clients'' teams are trained on how to sustain the results. As a team of experienced hospital and physician practice operators, we''ve been in your shoes and know your struggles. We use a three-pronged approach that includes operational and process best practices, analytics and technology to craft a comprehensive solution. We''ll focus on your hospital reaching its operational and financial goals so you can focus on your patients, families and community.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Collaborative Partnership</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>As experienced hospital operators, our consultants will become familiar with your current operations to provide tangible, action-oriented solutions and ensure results are realized. Everything we do, from our end-to-end revenue cycle assessments to conversion assistance, is all about partnership and long-term results. We work with clients to identify areas for improvement and help them hardwire the operational solutions needed to sustain success while at the same time providing tangible financial results for the project at hand.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//consulting/">Read more about our partnership model</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Revenue Cycle Support Services</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We go beyond what you expect from business office outsourced services. Our model is unique‚Äîin addition to traditional transactional-based services such as complex claims resolution, AR management and denials management, we dive deeper to find the root cause of the denial or other issue, not just fix current transaction. Your long-term success is our goal.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//revenue-cycle-support-services/">Read more about revenue cycle support services</a></p>\r\n</div>', 'Products & Services', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'products-services', '', '', '2017-10-05 07:11:32', '2017-10-05 07:11:32', '', 0, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//?page_id=12', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(13, 1, '2017-10-04 11:55:30', '2017-10-04 11:55:30', '', 'Products & Services', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '12-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-04 11:55:30', '2017-10-04 11:55:30', '', 12, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//2017/10/04/12-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(14, 1, '2017-10-04 11:55:37', '2017-10-04 11:55:37', '<div class="cushycms"><h1>Experienced leaders, driving results</h1>\r\n\r\n<p class="emphasized">We''re passionate about building long-term relationships with our clients. Based on your specific needs, our operational experts will complete a comprehensive assessment of the current operation, make recommendations and define a road map to accomplish the financial and operational goals that are a priority to you.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nWe also can provide experienced operators on an interim basis to serve as patient access or revenue cycle leadership within your organization‚Äîfocusing on process redesign, best practice operational models, patient experience or associate training and development programs.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="emphasized"><strong>How can we partner with your organization?</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Patient access best practice optimization</li>\r\n	<li>Patient access service excellence training</li>\r\n	<li>HIM optimization and centralization</li>\r\n	<li>Development of centralized business office and patient access centralized scheduling</li>\r\n	<li>RCM process optimization</li>\r\n	<li>End-to-end revenue cycle gap analysis</li>\r\n	<li>Vendor management\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Improving yield</li>\r\n		<li>Reducing costs</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<!--<li>ICD-10 preparation</li>-->\r\n	<li>EMR integration operations support</li>\r\n	<li>Revenue cycle systems selection and implementation support</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Collaborative partnership for every engagement is the key to optimizing operational efficiency<br>\r\nwhile decreasing costs.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="cta"><a href="http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//contact/">Contact us today</a> for an end-to-end revenue cycle assessment,<br>\r\ncall us 704-765-3715 or come by our office at:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n9713 Northcross Center Ct, Suite 301<br>\r\nHuntersville, NC 28017</p>\r\n</div>', 'Consulting', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'consulting', '', '', '2017-10-05 07:14:44', '2017-10-05 07:14:44', '', 0, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//?page_id=14', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(15, 1, '2017-10-04 11:55:37', '2017-10-04 11:55:37', '', 'Consulting', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '14-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-04 11:55:37', '2017-10-04 11:55:37', '', 14, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//2017/10/04/14-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(16, 1, '2017-10-04 11:55:44', '2017-10-04 11:55:44', '<div class="cushycms"><h1>More than transactional support</h1>\r\n\r\n<p class="emphasized">Our team treats your hospital''s receivables as if they were their own. So instead of just managing the transactions themselves, our leaders identify ways to improve transaction efficiency for the long term, finding ways to prevent upstream errors and red flags before they occur. Over the term of our engagement, we help our clients by building a tool kit that provides resources and solutions to the opportunities identified in the accounts receivable.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our revenue cycle support services&nbsp;include:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Revenue integrity, e.g., charge capture and CDM services</li>\r\n	<li>Managed Care/Commercial Payor strategic contract analysis</li>\r\n	<li>Complex claims, denial and underpayment recovery services</li>\r\n	<li>Appeals requiring clinical and legal resources</li>\r\n	<li>Cash flow acceleration projects with root cause analysis</li>\r\n	<li>Coding review</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Why settle for short-term solutions? We want to partner with your organization to manage your transactional needs while suggesting improvements for long term, sustainable results.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="cta"><a href="http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//contact/">Contact us today</a> for an end-to-end revenue cycle assessment,<br>\r\ncall us 704-765-3715 or come by our office at:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n9713 Northcross Center Ct, Suite 301<br>\r\nHuntersville, NC 28017</p>\r\n</div>', 'Revenue Cycle Support Services', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'revenue-cycle-support-services', '', '', '2017-10-05 07:16:05', '2017-10-05 07:16:05', '', 0, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//?page_id=16', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(17, 1, '2017-10-04 11:55:44', '2017-10-04 11:55:44', '', 'Revenue Cycle Support Services', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '16-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-04 11:55:44', '2017-10-04 11:55:44', '', 16, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//2017/10/04/16-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(18, 1, '2017-10-04 11:55:49', '2017-10-04 11:55:49', '<div class="cushycms">\r\n        \r\n            <h1>The latest in healthcare news</h1>\r\n            <p class="emphasized">\r\n            	If there''s one constant in healthcare, it''s change. To help you stay on top of the latest developments and trends, we''ve collected the latest industry news and the developments from Ensemble Health Partners. \r\n            </p>\r\n            <div class="half-column cta">\r\n                <h2><a href="http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//industry-news/">Industry News</a></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="half-column cta">\r\n                <h2><a href="http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//ensemble-news/">Press</a></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="clear"></div>\r\n            \r\n        </div>', 'News', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'news', '', '', '2017-10-05 07:19:19', '2017-10-05 07:19:19', '', 0, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//?page_id=18', 0, 'page', '', 0),
