(24, 1, '2017-10-04 11:56:08', '2017-10-04 11:56:08', '<h1 class="cushycms" title="Main Header">Ensemble Careers</h1>\r\n\r\n                    <p class="emphasized cushycms" title="Description">Ensemble Health Partners is dedicated to providing our clients with experienced healthcare finance and revenue cycle professionals. We believe that our core values of trust, integrity, loyalty and service married with the belief that our work is worthwhile helps us build and sustain sincere relationships with our associates and clients. If you are a passionate, dedicated and experienced revenue cycle, consulting or finance professional and seek career and personal growth, we would love to hear from you. We believe we foster an environment where talented individuals can excel and shine. Our team believes that people are the most important part of our success and that when we take care of our people, they pay it forward by providing our clients with excellent results and world-class service.</p>\r\n\r\n                    <h2 class="cushycms" title="Secondary Header">How do I apply and what should I expect?</h2>\r\n\r\n                    <p class="emphasized cushycms" title="Description">You can apply by <a href="https://ts.tgsnapshot.com/signup.cfm?DL=3858" target="_blank">clicking here</a>, find out more by attending one of our <a href="http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//events/">Open House/Career Fairs</a> or read more about our open positions below and apply directly.<br />\r\n                        <br />\r\n                        Through the interview process, you will have the opportunity to speak with multiple members of management, be given plenty of time to discuss your passion and career goals and ultimately to connect future managers to your previous managers through our reference program. We apply Topgrading principles in our <a href="http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//culture/">hiring process</a> because we believe every new team member is worth taking the time to get to know. By the time you hit the floor, we''d like you to know enough about us that you are as excited as we are about the opportunities available within Ensemble.<br />\r\n                    </p>\r\n[opurtunities-list]', 'Careers', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'careers', '', '', '2017-10-07 07:19:56', '2017-10-07 07:19:56', '', 0, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//?page_id=24', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(25, 1, '2017-10-04 11:56:08', '2017-10-04 11:56:08', '', 'Careers', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '24-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-04 11:56:08', '2017-10-04 11:56:08', '', 24, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//2017/10/04/24-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(26, 1, '2017-10-04 11:56:12', '2017-10-04 11:56:12', '<div class="cushycms"><h1>Why Join Ensemble?</h1>\r\n\r\n<p class="emphasized">Ensemble Health Partner‚Äôs company Mission is to create real value for our clients ‚Äî empowering them to deliver the absolute best in clinical care, customer service and community engagement ‚Äî by partnering with them and enabling them to realize their maximum sustainable financial and operational goals.\r\n<br><br>As an employer, <i>our mission is to empower every member of our team to realize their maximum professional potential and create an environment conducive to our shared success.</i> As we look to partner with clients and add value, we also look to add value to our growing team by hiring the brightest minds in the business. We truly understand that our most valuable assets are our team members. Ensemble started with a core group of experienced Healthcare Revenue Cycle <a href="http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//our-team/">Leaders</a> committed to building a company around passionate, career-driven people and we are proud to boast an organization comprised of them.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style="font-size: 1.3em;">Or, in case you prefer bullet points:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul style="font-size: 1.2em;">\r\n	<li><b>It all starts as an idea.</b><br>\r\n	Ensemble Health Partners was built by an <a href="http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//our-team/">entrepreneur</a>, who believed that better service and better results were available to healthcare organizations ‚Äî so he created a company to provide that to clients. That has defined our company culture. We encourage ideas and process innovation. If a process could improve, let us know!\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><b>Ownership ‚Äî ‚ÄòYou‚Äôre the boss of that‚Äô ‚Äî Model</b><br>\r\n	No matter what position you may be hired into, you were hired because we believe you can own that position. At Ensemble, we expect you to own the process, create opportunities using the provided resources and develop your leadership skills.\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><b>Everyone puts their pants on one leg at a time.</b><br>\r\n	Our leadership are working managers, which means they work alongside you every day. They are leaders because of their passion for what they do and for helping others achieve excellent results. Ultimately, we would like for you to catch that same fire, so our structure is designed to be accessible. Everyone has access to leaders to promote career development and a 360 degree understanding of the business.\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><b>We believe in measurable results and measurable rewards.</b><br>\r\n	We believe in providing measurable results for our clients and that those results begin on our desks every day. We monitor accomplishments and quality in real-time and believe the <a href="http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//benefits/">incentives</a> for great performance should be in real-time as well.\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><b>Limits are for credit cards, not for careers.</b><br>\r\n	At Ensemble we don‚Äôt limit our growth, so we don‚Äôt want to limit yours either. Find out more by attending one of our <a href="http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//events/">Open House/Career Fairs</a> or <a href="https://workforcenow.adp.com/jobs/apply/posting.html?client=ercp&amp;jobId=67727&amp;lang=en_US&amp;source=CC3#" target="_blank">click here to apply now</a>.\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<span id="process"></span>\r\n<h2>Ensemble Health Partners Commitment to Top Performers:</h2>\r\n\r\n<p class="emphasized">As a Topgrading company, our hiring process is unusually thorough. We conduct chronological Topgrading Interviews in which we ask about your entire career and are eager to learn about the successes, mistakes, key decisions and key relationships that have made you the professional you are today. Finalists for any position will be asked to arrange personal reference calls with former managers.\r\n<br><br>The benefits to high performers who apply are multi-faceted: (a) you will join a family with almost all high performers, (b) Ensemble‚Äôs high performers continue to grow the company and (c) the growth of the company provides continual opportunities for high performers to take the next step in their career without having to move organizations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="cta"><a href="https://workforcenow.adp.com/jobs/apply/posting.html?client=ercp&amp;jobId=67727&amp;lang=en_US&amp;source=CC3#" target="_blank">Apply now</a> or <a href="http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//">continue to open positions</a> to view our current opportunities.\r\n</p>\r\n</div>', 'Culture', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'culture', '', '', '2017-10-07 07:33:07', '2017-10-07 07:33:07', '', 0, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//?page_id=26', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(27, 1, '2017-10-04 11:56:12', '2017-10-04 11:56:12', '', 'Culture', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '26-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-04 11:56:12', '2017-10-04 11:56:12', '', 26, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//2017/10/04/26-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(28, 1, '2017-10-04 11:56:18', '2017-10-04 11:56:18', '<div class="cushycms"><h1>Benefits</h1>\r\n\r\n<h2>Health and Life-style Benefits:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Medical Insurance ‚Äì Optional high and low plan, designed to fit your budget and healthcare needs</li>\r\n	<li>Dental Insurance - Optional</li>\r\n	<li>Vision Insurance - Optional</li>\r\n	<li>Employee Assistance Program ‚Äì Company Paid</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Finances:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>401(k) plan available through ADP</li>\r\n	<li>Life Insurance ‚Äì Company Sponsored</li>\r\n	<li>Long-Term Disability ‚Äì Company Sponsored</li>\r\n	<li>Flexible Spending Account</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Benefits designed to help you get through the Mondays:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><b>Here We Grow</b> - We Love Referrals - earn up to $500 when we hire a candidate you referred</li>\r\n	<li><b>Pay it Forward</b> - Monthly and Quarterly Incentive Programs built around performance and quality</li>\r\n	<li><b>Most Wanted</b>&nbsp;-&nbsp;Our Bounty Account incentive program</li>\r\n	<li><b>For the Good</b> - Donate to team voted charities and the team fund to wear jeans on Thursdays and Fridays</li>\r\n	<li><b>Consistency is Key -&nbsp;</b>Earn up to two additional Personal Days for Perfect Attendance</li>\r\n	<li>Paid Time Off</li>\r\n	<li>Holiday Pay</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p class="cta"><a href="http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//culture/">Click here</a> to learn more about our Culture, or find out more by attending one of our <a href="http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//events/">Open House/Career Fairs</a>.</p>\r\n</div>', 'Benefits', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'benefits', '', '', '2017-10-07 07:29:13', '2017-10-07 07:29:13', '', 0, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//?page_id=28', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(29, 1, '2017-10-04 11:56:18', '2017-10-04 11:56:18', '', 'Benefits', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '28-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-04 11:56:18', '2017-10-04 11:56:18', '', 28, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//2017/10/04/28-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(30, 1, '2017-10-04 11:56:24', '2017-10-04 11:56:24', '<div class="cushycms"><h1>Events</h1>\r\n\r\n                        <h2>Open Houses and Career Fairs:</h2>\r\n\r\n                        <p class="emphasized">Ensemble Health Partners periodically holds open houses and career fairs for interested candidates that would like to come by and <a href="http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//culture/">see what we are all about</a>. We would love to meet you.<br>\r\n                            <br>\r\n                            These events are designed to introduce candidates to our organization, giving you a chance to hear what we like about working for Ensemble, see our facility and meet our <a href="http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//our-team/">leadership</a>. We will have stations for completion of applications if you have not already applied, some assessments that cover industry topics and the opportunity to interview for openings right on the spot.<br>\r\n                            &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n                        <h2>Location and Times:</h2>\r\n\r\n                        <p class="emphasized" style="border-bottom: 0;">There are no currently scheduled job fairs or events. Please check back later for more options.</p>\r\n                        <!--<p class="emphasized" style="border-bottom: 0;">Please join us for a career information session at CPCC:</p>\r\n                        \r\n                        <div class="cta"><strong>February 24</strong><br />\r\n                        CPCC Marancas Campus, Huntersville, NC<br />\r\n                        Claudia Watkins Belk Center Building, Room 131</div>\r\n                        \r\n                        <p class="emphasized" style="border-bottom: 0;">Reserve your space today by calling <strong>980-231-4080.</strong><br />\r\n                        <br />\r\n                        Please dress appropriately and be prepared for an interview. Must be 18 years of age.</p>\r\n                        \r\n                        <hr />--></div>', 'Events', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'events', '', '', '2017-10-07 07:25:42', '2017-10-07 07:25:42', '', 0, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//?page_id=30', 0, 'page', '', 0),
