(113, 1, '2017-10-05 05:14:59', '2017-10-05 05:14:59', '<div class="cushycms"><h1>Solutions born from experience, not theory</h1>\r\n\r\n<p class="emphasized">Our vision is to spur innovation within revenue cycle using a proven operational model, paired with technology, to provide predictable, actionable and solution-driven approaches to the complex issues of revenue cycle.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Pressure on hospitals has never been greater.</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The shift of responsibility from payor to patient in the form of higher out-of-pocket costs</li>\r\n	<li>Reimbursement rate reductions from all payor sources</li>\r\n	<li>High fixed and variable costs</li>\r\n	<li>Patient satisfaction and its impact on future reimbursement rates</li>\r\n	<li>The rapid evolution toward&nbsp;value-based reimbursement models of the future</li>\r\n	<li>Maintaining compliance with a shifting regulatory landscape</li>\r\n	<li>Improving clinical outcomes and the quality of care delivered</li>\r\n	<li>The need for providers to increase operational efficiencies</li>\r\n	<li>Revenue leakage</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>All of our associates have earned the Certified Revenue Cycle Representatives designation from HFMA, and we use Lean Six Sigma methodologies. We take a three-pronged approach‚Äîoperational and process best practices, analytics and technology‚Äîto every challenge, which allows us to see the big picture and ensure the upstream processes are corrected and our clients know how to sustain the results. Collaborative partnership allows us to focus on our client''s operational and financial goals while allowing them to focus their time and resources on caring for patients, families and communities.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="half-column cta">\r\n<h2>Our Story</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We''ve been on your side. Now we''re leveraging our expertise to help hospitals and providers.  <a href="our-story.php">Read more.</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="half-column cta">\r\n<h2>Our Team</h2>\r\n\r\n<p