(142, 1, '2017-10-05 06:00:07', '2017-10-05 06:00:07', 'Lane brings a unique background of managed care, IT, finance and revenue cycle to Ensemble Health Partners, where he is responsible for accounts receivable management and root cause analysis related to payor analytics, denials, underpayments and appeals. In previous positions he established a national underpayment/payment compliance team responsible for the resolution of contractual underpayments. Lane also helped design, build and grow a comprehensive contract management system to identify and track payment discrepancies. Lane and his team were responsible for not only the recovery of millions in underpaid claims but also in the resolution of facility and payor specific issues that ultimately increase downstream revenue.', 'Lane Rosenthal CRCR, MBA', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'lane-rosenthal-crcr-mba', '', '', '2017-10-05 06:00:07', '2017-10-05 06:00:07', '', 0, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//?post_type=team&#038;p=142', 0, 'team', '', 0),
