(149, 1, '2017-10-05 06:02:45', '2017-10-05 06:02:45', 'Brad specializes in managed care and revenue cycle operations. He has a strong background in managed care contracting and implementation, from both the payor and provider side. Additionally, he is proficient in leveraging organizational opportunities to negotiate the best possible contract for his clients. As a senior director with Healthcare MCR in Cleveland, Ohio, Brad''s hands-on knowledge and experience touched each aspect of the revenue cycle. Brad''s experience with new acquisition hospitals has proven extremely valuable to his clients as he has worked with a number of hospitals: to increase EBITDA, establish operational processes and cost efficiencies, and to help navigate contract negotiations.', 'Bradley Gingerich CRCR', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bradley-gingerich-crcr', '', '', '2017-10-05 06:02:45', '2017-10-05 06:02:45', '', 0, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//?post_type=team&#038;p=149', 0, 'team', '', 0),
