(152, 1, '2017-10-05 06:03:34', '2017-10-05 06:03:34', 'Toni Hatch is the VP of Education and Training at Ensemble Health Partners (EHP). She joined EHP in 2015 and has more than 30 years of healthcare management experience in both for-profit and not-for-profit systems.\r\n \r\nPrior to joining EHP, Toni was with HMA, Triad Hospital and Community Health Systems in revenue cycle leadership roles. During her career she has held various Business Office Director positions in North Carolina, Iowa, Illinois and Kentucky. \r\n \r\nToni is an active member in the American Association of Healthcare Administrative Management (AAHAM) and the Healthcare Financial Management Association (HFMA), and had previously earned the Certified Patient Account Manager (CPAM) and is currently a Certified Patient Account Technician (CPAT). \r\n                  \r\nToni holds a degree in liberal arts from Gaston College in North Carolina. Gardening, reading and watching college football top the list of her favorite activities!   ', 'Toni Hatch CPAT', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'toni-hatch-cpat', '', '', '2017-10-05 06:03:34', '2017-10-05 06:03:34', '', 0, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//?post_type=team&#038;p=152', 0, 'team', '', 0),
