(154, 1, '2017-10-05 06:04:35', '2017-10-05 06:04:35', 'Stanley leads the day-to-day operations of our Client Service Center. Stanley brings to Ensemble Health 20-plus years of revenue cycle leadership experience. He has established a strong track record in billing compliance with an emphasis on reducing bad debt and accounts receivable days. Most recently, he was vice president, Shared Services, for Community Health Systems, where he was responsible for building and managing a nine-hospital service center spanning 5 states. Responsibilities included pre-arrival, billing, insurance follow up, cash posting, insurance follow up, and denial management. He has also proven his ability to lead as he coordinated and assisted in approximately 15 new hospital acquisitions, working to retrain staff and ensure a seamless transition to a new software platform. Stanley is able to motivate and guide revenue cycle staff while building a solid team environment by emphasizing a superior work ethic and commitment to customer service excellence.', 'Stanley Hester CRCR', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'stanley-hester-crcr', '', '', '2017-10-05 06:04:35', '2017-10-05 06:04:35', '', 0, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//?post_type=team&#038;p=154', 0, 'team', '', 0),
