(157, 1, '2017-10-05 06:05:15', '2017-10-05 06:05:15', 'David assists clients with implementing best practice billing and collections operations to generate improved cash flows and revenue cycle operational efficiencies. David brings to Ensemble Health Partners a diverse background and experience throughout multiple areas of revenue cycle including patient access, cash posting, billing, and accounts receivable. He has previously served as a business office director, director of accounts receivable for a 23 hospital shared service center and most recently as a director of revenue cycle services for a large national revenue cycle company. David has proven his ability to develop processes using innovation to reduce costs and improve collections resulting in long-term increased performance.', 'David Hitzel', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'david-hitzel', '', '', '2017-10-05 06:05:15', '2017-10-05 06:05:15', '', 0, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//?post_type=team&#038;p=157', 0, 'team', '', 0),
