(159, 1, '2017-10-05 06:06:20', '2017-10-05 06:06:20', 'As a healthcare business consultant, Jenna brings 18 years of progressive experience in healthcare information management, including HIM coding, operations, general management, education, quality management and revenue cycle. Her strengths include standardizing HIM processes, implementation project management and revenue cycle operations. Jenna has worked with hospitals to standardize their HIM workflow and create significant cost savings. She is committed to teamwork and promoting directives that meet urgent medical record operation needs through the highest level of quality, accuracy and customer service. Jenna is a familiar presenter at industry webinars and conferences.', 'Jenna Jordan, RHIA', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'jenna-jordan-rhia', '', '', '2017-10-05 06:06:20', '2017-10-05 06:06:20', '', 0, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//?post_type=team&#038;p=159', 0, 'team', '', 0),
