(162, 1, '2017-10-05 06:07:05', '2017-10-05 06:07:05', 'As Vice President of Consulting Services, Lori is responsible for the continued development of our consulting services. Lori brings 20 plus years of progressive leadership experience in revenue cycle management, including patient access, billing, collections, cash posting, managed care, customer service and credit balance management. Prior to joining Ensemble Health Partners in spring 2015, Lori held many roles within the healthcare revenue cycle, including Business Office Director, Patient Access Director and Divisional Director of Patient Financial Services. During her time in those roles, Lori spearheaded the consolidation of two business offices and coordinated the training and seamless transition of 11 newly acquired hospitals into a single software platform. Lori''s extensive experience within the healthcare revenue cycle and proven ability to improve accounts receivable metrics recommend her to lead our clients to the same success.', 'Lori Norton', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'lori-norton', '', '', '2017-10-05 06:07:05', '2017-10-05 06:07:05', '', 0, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//?post_type=team&#038;p=162', 0, 'team', '', 0),
