(168, 1, '2017-10-05 07:10:47', '2017-10-05 07:10:47', '<div class="cushycms"><h1>Proven solutions</h1>\r\n\r\n<p class="emphasized">Unlike the traditional consulting or contingency model, we partner with your hospital to go beyond the operational task at hand, and we help our clients by ensuring the upstream processes are identified and that our clients'' teams are trained on how to sustain the results. As a team of experienced hospital and physician practice operators, we''ve been in your shoes and know your struggles. We use a three-pronged approach that includes operational and process best practices, analytics and technology to craft a comprehensive solution. We''ll focus on your hospital reaching its operational and financial goals so you can focus on your patients, families and community.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Collaborative Partnership</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>As experienced hospital operators, our consultants will become familiar with your current operations to provide tangible, action-oriented solutions and ensure results are realized. Everything we do, from our end-to-end revenue cycle assessments to conversion assistance, is all about partnership and long-term results. We work with clients to identify areas for improvement and help them hardwire the operational solutions needed to sustain success while at the same time providing tangible financial results for the project at hand.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="consulting.php">Read more about our partnership model</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Revenue Cycle Support Services</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We go beyond what you expect from business office outsourced services. Our model is unique‚Äîin addition to traditional transactional-based services such as complex claims resolution, AR management and denials management, we dive deeper to find the root cause of the denial or other issue, not just fix current transaction. Your long-term success is our goal.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="integrated-support-services.php">Read more about revenue cycle support services</a></p>\r\n</div>', 'Products & Services', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '12-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-05 07:10:47', '2017-10-05 07:10:47', '', 12, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//12-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(169, 1, '2017-10-05 07:11:32', '2017-10-05 07:11:32', '<div class="cushycms"><h1>Proven solutions</h1>\r\n\r\n<p class="emphasized">Unlike the traditional consulting or contingency model, we partner with your hospital to go beyond the operational task at hand, and we help our clients by ensuring the upstream processes are identified and that our clients'' teams are trained on how to sustain the results. As a team of experienced hospital and physician practice operators, we''ve been in your shoes and know your struggles. We use a three-pronged approach that includes operational and process best practices, analytics and technology to craft a comprehensive solution. We''ll focus on your hospital reaching its operational and financial goals so you can focus on your patients, families and community.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Collaborative Partnership</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>As experienced hospital operators, our consultants will become familiar with your current operations to provide tangible, action-oriented solutions and ensure results are realized. Everything we do, from our end-to-end revenue cycle assessments to conversion assistance, is all about partnership and long-term results. We work with clients to identify areas for improvement and help them hardwire the operational solutions needed to sustain success while at the same time providing tangible financial results for the project at hand.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//consulting/">Read more about our partnership model</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Revenue Cycle Support Services</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We go beyond what you expect from business office outsourced services. Our model is unique‚Äîin addition to traditional transactional-based services such as complex claims resolution, AR management and denials management, we dive deeper to find the root cause of the denial or other issue, not just fix current transaction. Your long-term success is our goal.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//revenue-cycle-support-services/">Read more about revenue cycle support services</a></p>\r\n</div>', 'Products & Services', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '12-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-05 07:11:32', '2017-10-05 07:11:32', '', 12, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//12-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(170, 1, '2017-10-05 07:13:08', '2017-10-05 07:13:08', '<div class="cushycms"><h1>Experienced leaders, driving results</h1>\n\n<p class="emphasized">We''re passionate about building long-term relationships with our clients. Based on your specific needs, our operational experts will complete a comprehensive assessment of the current operation, make recommendations and define a road map to accomplish the financial and operational goals that are a priority to you.<br>\n<br>\nWe also can provide experienced operators on an interim basis to serve as patient access or revenue cycle leadership within your organization‚Äîfocusing on process redesign, best practice operational models, patient experience or associate training and development programs.</p>\n\n<h2 class="emphasized"><strong>How can we partner with your organization?</strong></h2>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Patient access best practice optimization</li>\n	<li>Patient access service excellence training</li>\n	<li>HIM optimization and centralization</li>\n	<li>Development of centralized business office and patient access centralized scheduling</li>\n	<li>RCM process optimization</li>\n	<li>End-to-end revenue cycle gap analysis</li>\n	<li>Vendor management\n	<ul>\n		<li>Improving yield</li>\n		<li>Reducing costs</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<!--<li>ICD-10 preparation</li>-->\n	<li>EMR integration operations support</li>\n	<li>Revenue cycle systems selection and implementation support</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Collaborative partnership for every engagement is the key to optimizing operational efficiency<br>\nwhile decreasing costs.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class="cta"><a href="http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//contact/">Contact us today</a> for an end-to-end revenue cycle assessment,<br>\ncall us 704-765-3715 or come by our office at:<br>\n<br>\n9713 Northcross Center Ct, Suite 301<br>\nHuntersville, NC 28017</p>\n</div>', 'Consulting', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '14-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-10-05 07:13:08', '2017-10-05 07:13:08', '', 14, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//14-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(171, 1, '2017-10-05 07:13:25', '2017-10-05 07:13:25', '<div class="cushycms"><h1>Experienced leaders, driving results</h1>\r\n\r\n<p class="emphasized">We''re passionate about building long-term relationships with our clients. Based on your specific needs, our operational experts will complete a comprehensive assessment of the current operation, make recommendations and define a road map to accomplish the financial and operational goals that are a priority to you.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nWe also can provide experienced operators on an interim basis to serve as patient access or revenue cycle leadership within your organization‚Äîfocusing on process redesign, best practice operational models, patient experience or associate training and development programs.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="emphasized"><strong>How can we partner with your organization?</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Patient access best practice optimization</li>\r\n	<li>Patient access service excellence training</li>\r\n	<li>HIM optimization and centralization</li>\r\n	<li>Development of centralized business office and patient access centralized scheduling</li>\r\n	<li>RCM process optimization</li>\r\n	<li>End-to-end revenue cycle gap analysis</li>\r\n	<li>Vendor management\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Improving yield</li>\r\n		<li>Reducing costs</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<!--<li>ICD-10 preparation</li>-->\r\n	<li>EMR integration operations support</li>\r\n	<li>Revenue cycle systems selection and implementation support</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Collaborative partnership for every engagement is the key to optimizing operational efficiency<br>\r\nwhile decreasing costs.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="cta"><a href="http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//contact/">Contact us today</a> for an end-to-end revenue cycle assessment,<br>\r\ncall us 704-765-3715 or come by our office at:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n9713 Northcross Center Ct, Suite 301<br>\r\nHuntersville, NC 28017</p>\r\n</div>', 'Consulting', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '14-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-05 07:13:25', '2017-10-05 07:13:25', '', 14, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//14-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(172, 1, '2017-10-05 07:15:00', '2017-10-05 07:15:00', '', 'Revenue Cycle Support Services', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '16-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-10-05 07:15:00', '2017-10-05 07:15:00', '', 16, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//16-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(173, 1, '2017-10-05 07:15:47', '2017-10-05 07:15:47', '<div class="cushycms"><h1>More than transactional support</h1>\r\n\r\n<p class="emphasized">Our team treats your hospital''s receivables as if they were their own. So instead of just managing the transactions themselves, our leaders identify ways to improve transaction efficiency for the long term, finding ways to prevent upstream errors and red flags before they occur. Over the term of our engagement, we help our clients by building a tool kit that provides resources and solutions to the opportunities identified in the accounts receivable.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our revenue cycle support services&nbsp;include:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Revenue integrity, e.g., charge capture and CDM services</li>\r\n	<li>Managed Care/Commercial Payor strategic contract analysis</li>\r\n	<li>Complex claims, denial and underpayment recovery services</li>\r\n	<li>Appeals requiring clinical and legal resources</li>\r\n	<li>Cash flow acceleration projects with root cause analysis</li>\r\n	<li>Coding review</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Why settle for short-term solutions? We want to partner with your organization to manage your transactional needs while suggesting improvements for long term, sustainable results.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="cta"><a href="contact/">Contact us today</a> for an end-to-end revenue cycle assessment,<br>\r\ncall us 704-765-3715 or come by our office at:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n9713 Northcross Center Ct, Suite 301<br>\r\nHuntersville, NC 28017</p>\r\n</div>', 'Revenue Cycle Support Services', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '16-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-05 07:15:47', '2017-10-05 07:15:47', '', 16, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//16-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(174, 1, '2017-10-05 07:16:05', '2017-10-05 07:16:05', '<div class="cushycms"><h1>More than transactional support</h1>\r\n\r\n<p class="emphasized">Our team treats your hospital''s receivables as if they were their own. So instead of just managing the transactions themselves, our leaders identify ways to improve transaction efficiency for the long term, finding ways to prevent upstream errors and red flags before they occur. Over the term of our engagement, we help our clients by building a tool kit that provides resources and solutions to the opportunities identified in the accounts receivable.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our revenue cycle support services&nbsp;include:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Revenue integrity, e.g., charge capture and CDM services</li>\r\n	<li>Managed Care/Commercial Payor strategic contract analysis</li>\r\n	<li>Complex claims, denial and underpayment recovery services</li>\r\n	<li>Appeals requiring clinical and legal resources</li>\r\n	<li>Cash flow acceleration projects with root cause analysis</li>\r\n	<li>Coding review</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Why settle for short-term solutions? We want to partner with your organization to manage your transactional needs while suggesting improvements for long term, sustainable results.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="cta"><a href="http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//contact/">Contact us today</a> for an end-to-end revenue cycle assessment,<br>\r\ncall us 704-765-3715 or come by our office at:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n9713 Northcross Center Ct, Suite 301<br>\r\nHuntersville, NC 28017</p>\r\n</div>', 'Revenue Cycle Support Services', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '16-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-05 07:16:05', '2017-10-05 07:16:05', '', 16, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//16-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
