(299, 1, '2017-10-05 10:10:00', '2017-10-05 10:10:00', 'Ensemble Health Partners is pleased to announce Estelle Welte has joined the company as Senior Vice President, Client Engagement and Development. With more than 25 years of healthcare experience, Estelle is dedicated to results-driven service excellence.', 'Ensemble Health Partners Welcomes Estelle Welte to Team', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ensemble-health-partners-welcomes-estelle-welte-to-team', '', '', '2017-10-05 10:10:00', '2017-10-05 10:10:00', '', 0, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//?post_type=press&#038;p=299', 0, 'press', '', 0),
