(301, 1, '2017-10-05 10:10:16', '2017-10-05 10:10:16', 'Ensemble Health Partners is gaining ground in the Healthcare Revenue Cycle arena as well as among our Lake Norman Region.¬†Since locating an office in Huntersville, North Carolina in October of 2014, their on-site team has grown from four to 54 associates and continues to expand. Over the next two months, the local office will double in size, adding over 55 additional positions, an exciting development for Huntersville‚Äôs economy.', 'Ensemble Health Partners Growing in Huntersville', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ensemble-health-partners-growing-in-huntersville-2', '', '', '2017-10-05 10:33:14', '2017-10-05 10:33:14', '', 0, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//?post_type=press&#038;p=301', 0, 'press', '', 0),
