(303, 1, '2017-10-05 10:35:02', '2017-10-05 10:35:02', 'Ensemble Health Partners is pleased to announced that it was recently honored by the Lake Norman Chamber of Commerce for its efforts in diversity at the Lake Norman Chamber Diversity luncheon. The chamber selected Ensemble Health Partners as one of its Corporate Champions of Diversity finalists.', 'Ensemble Health Partners Named Corporate Champions of Diversity Finalists by Lake Norman Chamber of Commerce', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '294-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-10-05 10:35:02', '2017-10-05 10:35:02', '', 294, 'http://greenpagebd.com/ensemble//294-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
